Patterns of design. Homework No. 1.
Generating patterns. Singleton. Abstract factory. Published on January 12, 2019
Task 1. Use template Abstract Factory. Create a factory to create buttons and flags for Windows, Macintosh depending on user selection.
Create a Client class to check the work of the factories.
A class diagram like https://refactoring.guru/uk/design-patterns/abstract-factory

Task 2.
In the realization of the pattern abstract factory (Abstract factory) task 1 to make all the factories as Singleton (Singleton).
